<document>
    <properties>
        <title>FAQ</title>
    </properties>

    <body>
	<section name="Common Questions">
	<ol>
	<li><a href="#answer1">Why doesn't my method annotated with @TriggersRemove actually trigger a cache remove?</a></li>
	</ol>
	</section>
	
	<section name="Answers">
	<ol>
	<li name="answer1">Make sure your method annotated with @TriggersRemove has the same arguments (type, number, and order) as another @Cacheable method. Don't put
	@TriggersRemove on any method also marked @Cacheable, as it will do exactly that.</li>
	</ol>
	</section>
	</body>
</document>